Nov 9 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Fresenius SE, Siegfried Holding and Wartsila Oyj Abp, on Tuesday.


HIGHLIGHTS

* Fresenius SE FREG.DE: JP Morgan cuts to neutral from overweight

* Shell RDSa.L: HSBC raises to buy from hold

* Siegfried Holding AG SFZN.S: Credit Suisse assumes coverage with outperform rating

* Swedish Match AB SWMA.ST: JP Morgan cuts to underweight from neutral

* Wartsila Oyj Abp WRT1V.HE: HSBC raises to buy from hold
